1.下载FreeDos安装包，解压后得到freedos-img，进入文件夹将其中a.img的文件重命名为freedos.img。
2.使用bximage生成一个新的软盘映像起名为pm.img。
3.修改当前工作目录下的bochsrc配置文件
增加如下几行：
floppya: 1_44="freedos.img", status=inserted
floppyb: 1_44="pm.img", status=inserted
boot: a
4.启动bochs：bochs  -f  bochsrc，并且执行"c"
You can also start bochs with the -q option to skip these menus.

1. Restore factory default configuration
2. Read options from...
3. Edit options
4. Save options to...
5. Restore the Bochs state from...
6. Begin simulation
7. Quit now

Please choose one: [6] 
00000000000i[      ] installing x module as the Bochs GUI
00000000000i[      ] using log file bochsout.txt
Next at t=0
(0) [0x0000fffffff0] f000:fff0 (unk. ctxt): jmpf 0xf000:e05b          ; ea5be000f0
<bochs:1> b 0x7c00
<bochs:1> c

5.执行c命令之后，启动freedos，然后执行如下命令，格式化B盘并切换到B盘：
format.ext b:
b:

6.编译：
make pmtest6.com

7.将pmtest6.com复制到虚拟软驱pm.img中，执行make everything,包含具体命令如下：
1)sudo mkdir /mnt/floppy
2)sudo mount -o loop pm.img /mnt/floppy
3)sudo cp pmtest6.com   /mnt/floppy/
4)sudo umount/mnt/floppy 

8.在freedos B盘符下输入:\pmtest6.com

9.调试pmtest6.asm,需要添加相关代码：
1).pmtest6.asm:
org 0100h
++xchg bx,bx
jmp LABEL_BEGIN

添加之后需要重新:
make pmtest6.asm
make everything
bochs -f bochrc

2).bochs
++magic_break: enabled=1
# MAGIC_BREAK:
# This enables the "magic breakpoint" feature when using the debugger.
# The useless cpu instruction XCHG BX, BX causes Bochs to enter the
# debugger mode. This might be useful for software development.
